description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It also imports necessary dependencies such as React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React component tree into a container DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root container.
